milestones.description: Graham Gooch has broken the record for most sixes (8) in ODIs for ENG, going past Ian Botham's 7
Allan Border and Martin Kent's 74-run partnership is AUS's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 65 between Greg Chappell and Allan Border
